Package SOPIE
=============

Version 1.5, 2015-09-28
Added news information.
Changed dependencies and imports. Version 1.5 is dependent on circular and ADGofTest; and selectively imports stats, grDevices and graphics.
Added more references to documentation.
Utilise tests of uniformity from the circular(rayleigh.test) and ADGofTest(ad.test) packages.
Removed redundant variables in a.estimate and b.estimate functions.


Version 1.4, 2015-06-05
First release of the SOPIE package (Sequential off-pulse interval estimation).

